display="inline"><![CDATA[\prec \colon  A\mathbin {\nrightarrow } A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00NL.xml"
addr="jms-00NL"
title="Well-founded relation">well-founded</fr:link> if and only if there are no infinite descending <html:span
xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\prec ]]></fr:tex>-chains</html:span> in <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex>, i.e. no infinite sequences <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[a_0,a_1,\ldots ,a_i,\ldots ]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[a_0\succ  a_1\succ \cdots  a_i\succ \cdots ]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
